name: Age of Ascent (Canceled)
blurb: Age of Ascent is a new space MMO that lets thousands of people play together in realtime in the same battle.

rewards.reward: BACKER:  Thanks for your support + access to the private backer forums (all pledge levels get this)
RECORD BREAKER: Your name on the official Age of Ascent "Largest Videogame PvP Battle" record attempt roll call.
CUTTER: A backer-only cutter-class spaceship + Your choice of a set of "backer" decals for all of your spaceships.
SCOUT:  2x backer-only spaceships (scout and cutter-classes) + 500 ingame credits + Your choice of a set of "backer" decals for all of your spaceships.
